This version of the library is tested with SSD1306 controller installed in 
monochrome COG OLED 128x64 display UG-2864HSWEG01. You can find this display
at eBay from several sellers. You also can find this display in the monochrome 
128x64 OLED display from Adafruit.

The library is a siginificantly modified version of SSD1306 library from 
Adafruit: https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_SSD1306